      <h2 class="lg-section-headline" style="color:#faf7f2;">Give the baby their<br>own <em>.com.</em></h2>
      <p class="lg-section-sub" style="color:rgba(250,247,242,0.75);margin:0 auto 32px;">$29 introductory price. One-time. One full year for them, a printable certificate for you.</p>
      <a href="#buy" class="lg-hero-cta">Give the Gift — $29 →</a>
